history.content:
It should be fine - maybe just email your TA!

--------------------------------------------------------------

Most of the time, it's not that big a deal if you're still on the Piazza and Gradescope, as long as the class doesn't show up on your CalCentral.  To drop the Piazza, hit the little gear up in the top right of the screen and select "Account/Email Settings".  I believe there isn't a way for a student to drop themselves from Gradescope; if you really want it to go away for whatever reason, it's probably best to email the 161 staff / make a post on Piazza before you leave it.
It should be fine - maybe just email your TA!
